{"tid":2186708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"fb有心人每日整合方便轉發","createTime":"2020-09-03T06:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T08:22:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5d68802d61aae9bcaebfc0cddfc766fee72bbc","tid":2186708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/5D2LSXILRNB4VD7FAFPHOSFK64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2F5D2LSXILRNB4VD7FAFPHOSFK64%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hTnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=8264fcac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2F5D2LSXILRNB4VD7FAFPHOSFK64%2F&h=1b81b124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/5D2LSXILRNB4VD7FAFPHOSFK64/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nfb有心人每日整合方便轉發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eulPUiwy85QrxdjX2lH4kANioyc=/706x818/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LSKIWFU3GZEP7ILWDYWT5NXZL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeulPUiwy85QrxdjX2lH4kANioyc%3D%2F706x818%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLSKIWFU3GZEP7ILWDYWT5NXZL4.jpg&h=b902021e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「一日一蘋果」專頁由版主和女友兩人經營，每天花數小時整合廣告資訊。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》過去大半個月接獲的廣告五花八門，敢於「開名」如同另類立場認證，有人按圖索驥光顧商戶，支持黃色經濟圈。facebook專頁「一日一蘋果」每日出文介紹《蘋果》廣告，除相關廣告版面，更附上商戶聯絡資訊，並把部份廣告資訊轉回文字版，方便同路人轉發分享。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：分類廣告重生 創意搶眼球<br />\n<br />\n「一日一蘋果」專頁的版主向記者透露，專頁由他跟女友兩人經營，每天需花小時計整理資訊內容，「兩人處理最短試過兩個鐘，最耐嗰次係婚禮界嗰日（8月21日A1），用咗九個鐘。」但版主不諱言，尋找廣告客戶資料時，不免分心「追帖」追看商戶的舊帖文及了解其業務等，令「工時」拉長。<br />\n<br />\n他直言，當初除買報紙支持外，亦想支持落廣告的商戶，但發現紙本廣告跟網絡之間缺乏連結，「如果有人整合所有廣告，可以一目了然就好啦！」雖然當時已有人把這些商戶的連結分享，但方式未必長久，最終自己出手整合，「要親手逐頁睇，逐個廣告睇，感受佢哋嘅message（訊息），唔係流水式叫人like，希望令良心小店做嘅廣告有更好效果。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：波網：港隊處劣勢 打氣抗黑哨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惡法下社會情緒反彈<br />\n<br />\n中大新聞與傳播學院講師梁麗娟認為，...................................................；同樣情況九七前香港電影界亦有發生，電影人於是製作出大量劍走偏鋒、政治題材的電影作品如《表姐》系列，常見主角對抗惡勢力和命運的隱喻。<br />\n<br />\n她強調，商家在立場相近媒體賣廣告亦是商業考慮，因為接觸到的客戶政治光譜接近，而港人一直未忘反修例以來的種種，如連儂牆被毀等不同方式打壓，這次只是轉用《蘋果》作發聲表態平台。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報"},{"pid":"6af4f6f1bfe2c2b6c0bbbc0cc3143eef86973e08","tid":2186708,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日一蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Applertising/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplertising%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hTnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=6c3e7de0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Applertising/</a>"},{"pid":"f93773cc9b2601586e9270e283864a8682b623d9","tid":2186708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6af4f6f1bfe2c2b6c0bbbc0cc3143eef86973e08","tid":2186708,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日一蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Applertising/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplertising%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hTnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=6c3e7de0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Applertising/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:16:58.000Z","msg":"Pinned"},{"pid":"c35a3bfcf799a928446b64a898bde0ef261e31ff","tid":2186708,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor